# AJ Projects — API Key TODO Checklist
# Generated from aj-projects.config.json
# Fetch keys from these URLs and paste values into ~/aj-projects-skills/.env

## anthropic
- Where to get: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
- Env vars: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
- Needed by: AI & Agents
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## openai
- Where to get: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
- Env vars: OPENAI_API_KEY
- Needed by: AI & Agents, Media, Audio
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## gemini
- Where to get: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
- Env vars: GEMINI_API_KEY
- Needed by: AI & Agents
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## elevenlabs
- Where to get: https://elevenlabs.io/app/settings/api-keys
- Env vars: ELEVENLABS_API_KEY
- Needed by: Audio
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## figma
- Where to get: https://www.figma.com/settings -> Personal access tokens
- Env vars: FIGMA_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN
- Needed by: Design
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## notion
- Where to get: https://www.notion.so/profile/integrations
- Env vars: NOTION_API_KEY
- Needed by: Workspace, Productivity
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## supabase
- Where to get: https://supabase.com -> your project -> Settings -> API
- Env vars: SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
- Needed by: Engineering
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## n8n
- Where to get: Your n8n instance -> Settings -> n8n API
- Env vars: N8N_API_KEY
- Needed by: Automation
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## apify
- Where to get: https://console.apify.com/account/integrations
- Env vars: APIFY_TOKEN
- Needed by: Marketing, Sales
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## google_workspace
- Where to get: https://console.cloud.google.com -> APIs & Services -> Credentials -> OAuth 2.0 Client IDs
- Env vars: GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID
- Needed by: Workspace
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## stripe
- Where to get: https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
- Env vars: STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
- Needed by: Finance
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env

## salesforce
- Where to get: Salesforce Setup -> Identity -> My Profile -> Reset Security Token
- Env vars: SFDC_LOGIN_URL, SFDC_USERNAME, SFDC_PASSWORD, SFDC_SECURITY_TOKEN
- Needed by: Sales, Platform
- [ ] Obtained and pasted into .env
